<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Adın Soyadın — Portfolio</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;600&family=Montserrat:wght@200;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --gold: #C9A84C;
      --gold-light: #E8C96A;
      --gold-dim: #7a6228;
      --black: #080808;
      --black-mid: #111111;
      --black-soft: #1a1a1a;
      --white: #F5F0E8;
      --white-dim: #c0b8a8;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      cursor: none;
    }

    /* ── CUSTOM CURSOR ── */
    .cursor {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 12px; height: 12px;
      background: var(--gold);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      transition: transform .1s, background .2s;
    }
    .cursor-ring {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9998;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      transition: transform .25s ease, width .3s, height .3s, opacity .3s;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
    body:hover .cursor { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1); }

    /* ── NOISE OVERLAY ── */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none; z-index: 1000; opacity: .35;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 500;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 28px 60px;
      mix-blend-mode: normal;
      transition: background .4s, padding .4s;
    }
    nav.scrolled {
      background: rgba(8,8,8,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      padding: 18px 60px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: .22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white-dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      position: relative;
      transition: color .3s;
    }
    .nav-links a::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0;
      width: 0; height: 1px; background: var(--gold);
      transition: width .3s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    #hero {
      position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100vh;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-photo {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
      filter: brightness(.45) saturate(.6);
      transform: scale(1.05);
      animation: heroZoom 8s ease forwards;
    }
    @keyframes heroZoom {
      from { transform: scale(1.1); }
      to   { transform: scale(1.0); }
    }

    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(
        160deg,
        rgba(8,8,8,0.3) 0%,
        rgba(8,8,8,0.1) 40%,
        rgba(8,8,8,0.6) 100%
      );
    }

    .gold-line {
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%;
      width: 1px; height: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
      animation: lineDrop 1.6s .5s ease forwards;
    }
    @keyframes lineDrop {
      to { height: 100%; }
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 10;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeUp .9s 1s both;
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .68rem;
      letter-spacing: .38em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-name {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 8rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--white);
      text-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-name em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--white-dim);
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .72rem;
      letter-spacing: .26em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: color .4s;
    }
    .hero-cta::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: var(--gold);
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform .4s;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { color: var(--black); }
    .hero-cta:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .hero-cta span { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .scroll-indicator {
      position: absolute; bottom: 36px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      animation: fadeUp .8s 2s both;
    }
    .scroll-indicator span {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .6rem; letter-spacing: .3em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold-dim);
    }
    .scroll-arrow {
      width: 1px; height: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold-dim), transparent);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scrollPulse {
      0%,100% { opacity: .3; transform: scaleY(1); }
      50%      { opacity: 1;  transform: scaleY(1.2); }
    }

    /* ── ABOUT STRIP ── */
    #about {
      padding: 120px 60px;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px; align-items: center;
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .about-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .35em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;
    }
    .about-heading {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .about-heading em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .about-text {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--white-dim);
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .about-stats {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px; margin-top: 50px;
    }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--gold); line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .25em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--white-dim);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .about-img-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-img-wrap::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute;
      top: 20px; left: 20px; right: -20px; bottom: -20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    }
    .about-img-wrap img {
      width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4; object-fit: cover;
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      filter: saturate(.7) contrast(1.1);
    }

    /* ── SECTION HEADER ── */
    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 60px 80px;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .42em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
      display: block; margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .section-divider {
      width: 60px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold);
      margin: 28px auto 0;
    }

    /* ── PROJECTS ── */
    #projects {
      padding: 120px 60px;
      max-width: 1300px; margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .projects-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(340px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .project-card {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--black-mid);
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(60px);
      transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease, border-color .4s;
    }
    .project-card.visible {
      opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .project-card:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: .12s; }
    .project-card:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: .24s; }
    .project-card:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: .08s; }
    .project-card:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: .2s; }
    .project-card:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: .32s; }

    .project-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold-dim); }

    .project-img {
      width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 4/3; object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform .7s ease, filter .5s;
      filter: saturate(.5) brightness(.85);
    }
    .project-card:hover .project-img {
      transform: scale(1.06);
      filter: saturate(.8) brightness(1);
    }

    .project-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,8,8,0.9) 0%, transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0; transition: opacity .4s;
    }
    .project-card:hover .project-overlay { opacity: 1; }

    .project-info {
      padding: 28px 32px;
    }
    .project-tag {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .6rem; letter-spacing: .3em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 10px; display: block;
    }
    .project-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      transition: color .3s;
    }
    .project-card:hover .project-title { color: var(--gold-light); }
    .project-desc {
      font-size: 1rem; color: var(--white-dim);
      line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300;
    }
    .project-link {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 22px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .68rem; letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: gap .3s;
    }
    .project-link:hover { gap: 16px; }
    .project-link::after {
      content: '→'; font-size: .9rem;
    }

    /* FEATURED card */
    .project-card.featured {
      grid-column: span 2;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .project-card.featured .project-img {
      height: 100%; aspect-ratio: unset;
    }
    .project-card.featured .project-info {
      padding: 48px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    }
    .project-card.featured .project-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    /* ── SKILLS ── */
    #skills {
      padding: 100px 60px;
      background: var(--black-mid);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);
    }
    .skills-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 50px; margin-top: 0;
    }
    .skill-item {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px);
      transition: opacity .6s, transform .6s;
    }
    .skill-item.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .skill-item:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: .1s; }
    .skill-item:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: .2s; }
    .skill-item:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: .15s; }
    .skill-item:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: .25s; }
    .skill-item:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: .35s; }

    .skill-icon {
      font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 18px; display: block;
    }
    .skill-name {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold-light);
    }
    .skill-desc {
      font-size: .95rem; color: var(--white-dim);
      line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300;
    }
    .skill-bar-wrap {
      margin-top: 14px; height: 2px;
      background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    }
    .skill-bar {
      height: 100%; background: var(--gold);
      width: 0; transition: width 1.2s ease;
    }
    .skill-item.visible .skill-bar { width: var(--w); }

    /* ── CONTACT ── */
    #contact {
      padding: 140px 60px;
      text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    #contact::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .contact-inner { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
    .contact-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .contact-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .contact-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--white-dim);
      line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 52px;
    }
    .contact-email {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      transition: border-color .3s, color .3s;
      margin-bottom: 50px; display: block;
    }
    .contact-email:hover { color: var(--gold-light); border-color: var(--gold-light); }
    .contact-socials { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 32px; }
    .social-link {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white-dim); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color .3s;
    }
    .social-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      padding: 36px 60px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    }
    .footer-brand {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: .95rem; color: var(--gold-dim);
    }
    .footer-copy {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .62rem; letter-spacing: .2em;
      color: rgba(192,184,168,0.35);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── GOLD TICKER ── */
    .ticker-wrap {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
      padding: 14px 0;
      background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04);
    }
    .ticker-track {
      display: flex; gap: 60px;
      animation: ticker 22s linear infinite;
      width: max-content;
    }
    .ticker-item {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .68rem; letter-spacing: .35em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold-dim);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .ticker-dot { color: var(--gold); margin: 0 6px; }
    @keyframes ticker {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to   { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 22px 28px; }
      nav.scrolled { padding: 14px 28px; }
      .nav-links { gap: 22px; }
      #about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 80px 28px; gap: 48px; }
      .about-img-wrap { order: -1; }
      #projects { padding: 80px 28px; }
      .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .project-card.featured { grid-column: span 1; display: block; }
      .project-card.featured .project-img { aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
      #skills { padding: 80px 28px; }
      .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 36px; }
      #contact { padding: 100px 28px; }
      footer { padding: 28px; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
      .section-header { padding: 0 28px 60px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 580px) {
      .hero-name { font-size: 3rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- CURSOR -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">A.S.</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Hakkımda</a></li>
    <li><a href="#projects">Projeler</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Yetenekler</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">İletişim</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-photo"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="gold-line"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="hero-eyebrow">Portfolio — 2025</span>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Adın<br><em>Soyadın</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Tasarım, kod ve yaratıcılığın kesişiminde bir şeyler üretiyorum.</p>
    <a href="#projects" class="hero-cta"><span>Projelerimi Gör</span></a>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-indicator">
    <span>Kaydır</span>
    <div class="scroll-arrow"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TICKER -->
<div class="ticker-wrap">
  <div class="ticker-track">
    <span class="ticker-item">UI Tasarım<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Web Geliştirme<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Branding<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Ux Araştırma<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Mobil Uygulama<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Fotoğrafçılık<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Kreatif Yönetim<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">UI Tasarım<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Web Geliştirme<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Branding<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Ux Araştırma<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Mobil Uygulama<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Fotoğrafçılık<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
    <span class="ticker-item">Kreatif Yönetim<span class="ticker-dot">✦</span></span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div>
    <span class="about-label">Benim Hikayem</span>
    <h2 class="about-heading">Merhaba, ben<br><em>Adın Soyadın</em></h2>
    <p class="about-text">
      İstanbul merkezli bir tasarımcı ve geliştirici olarak, anlamlı dijital deneyimler yaratmak için yaratıcılığı ve teknolojiyi bir araya getiriyorum. Minimalist estetiğe ve güçlü hikaye anlatımına inanıyorum.
    </p>
    <p class="about-text" style="margin-top: 18px;">
      5+ yıldır markaların dijital kimliklerini şekillendiriyor, kullanıcıların hayatını kolaylaştıran ürünler tasarlıyorum.
    </p>
    <div class="about-stats">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">48+</div>
